{"tid":214256,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"清宿便靠1個動作 即瘦3kg 推介狂排便餐","createTime":"2017-04-23T16:21:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-24T19:12:34.000Z","uid":68110,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0cb54570c61c50c82af8cd3fbb92bc1f685a2787","tid":214256,"uid":68110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T16:21:19.000Z","msg":"招式1：日趴10分鐘 受便秘困擾50年的女士變日日有得痾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/2ad8251b8f59cee5622d174a09e4174b-1024x568_57229366058fb8dd5903bf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F04%2F2ad8251b8f59cee5622d174a09e4174b-1024x568_57229366058fb8dd5903bf.jpg&h=5ce07627&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以下方法由日本東邦大學附屬醫院綜合診療科教授-瓜田純久分享出來的。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/2fca0961-s_137419032458fb8debecf18.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F04%2F2fca0961-s_137419032458fb8debecf18.jpg&h=35ca642b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原理是利用趴下的動下以壓住腹部，從而刺激小腸各部份促進蠕動。<br />\n<br />\n不過這個方法有一個大原則，就是要確保腸道要有8小時空腹時間，即是說第一餐跟下一餐時間要有8小時不可進食（前一個天晚餐和隔天早餐次間一定有足夠時間）。因為人類的小腸要空腹8個小時才會開始蠕動，並把排泄物排出。而便秘的形成就是因為小腸和結直腸不蠕動。<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/48f0f4b70ac32090f03eb7840efd5fb5-373x507_78800350058fb8cd0ed691.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F04%2F48f0f4b70ac32090f03eb7840efd5fb5-373x507_78800350058fb8cd0ed691.jpg&h=f554574d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n步驟一：每天肚朝下方趴下10分鐘（可邊看電視、玩手機進行）。<br />\n步驟2：期間要左右翻滾身體5次。<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/04f0cb92-s_46306831558fb8e1556973.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F04%2F04f0cb92-s_46306831558fb8e1556973.jpg&h=dfb68ea3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n日本「便便博士」的辨野義己推薦 &lt; 周末排便法 Menu&gt;<br />\n這個餐單非常容易遵守，只需星期五、六晚進食便可，平日都可以如常進食其他食物。<br />\n<br />\n以下餐單的份量頗多的，如果一下子吃不完，可分兩次吃。<br />\n<br />\n星期五晚：乳酪250克、番薯500克（蒸熟後連皮吃）、蘋果2個<br />\n星期六晚：乳酪250克、番薯500克（蒸熟後連皮吃）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/img_36_148280212258fb9bd88c669.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F04%2Fimg_36_148280212258fb9bd88c669.png&h=3a0afafb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n辨野義己更實施了一年，在沒有任何節食的情況下，竟然能減掉11公斤，體脂從28％降低為21％，更能每天定時排便。<br />\n<br />\n進行以上兩個方法後，加上每天早上飲250ml溫水及於一日3餐中加入「生食調理法」，一定可以擺脫千年宿便的。<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/-2017-04-22-2.24.10_140822077358fb958ec086a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F04%2F-2017-04-22-2.24.10_140822077358fb958ec086a.png&h=b9e0f8c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n生食調理法非常簡單，只要在一日3餐中加入溫度不超過48度的蔬果便行。例如：蘋果、橙，一些沒有經高溫烹調的仍然保留原有酵素的蔬果。<br />\n<br />\n全文:<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nmplus.hk/lifestyle/%E5%AE%BF%E4%BE%BF-%E5%8B%95%E4%BD%9C-%E6%8E%92%E4%BE%BF/7/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nmplus.hk%2Flifestyle%2F%25E5%25AE%25BF%25E4%25BE%25BF-%25E5%258B%2595%25E4%25BD%259C-%25E6%258E%2592%25E4%25BE%25BF%2F7%2F&d=il%2BrReVPph3FBkDtfLAFOmxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=c417305c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nmplus.hk/lifestyle/%E5%AE%BF%E4%BE%BF-%E5%8B%95%E4%BD%9C-%E6%8E%92%E4%BE%BF/7/</a>"},{"pid":"3eb825a1419d0f84683b0d00e8610025086ecf1c","tid":214256,"uid":36866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T16:23:48.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"041f8de7a3cb615282f437cfe612d2ba4e59a75a","tid":214256,"uid":68110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T16:28:05.000Z","msg":"朝早賴床個時趴下碌下床就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇人一齊堅持一星期"},{"pid":"636abcbe1c3588eab929fc94fee8662bdb15cefa","tid":214256,"uid":68389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T04:43:22.000Z","msg":"原來沙灘個女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9504dc4023fdb5d6b4c7be1b8f596d1158ea6cda","tid":214256,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T05:05:04.000Z","msg":"諗起蘋果沙灘女<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a540e64b7e24138d9287be34c4077e4a3445120","tid":214256,"uid":68389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T19:05:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗起蘋果沙灘女<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇嚟佢應該成個肚都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9c84719e49eaea860601d3da1c56942c862f977","tid":214256,"uid":54490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T19:12:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}